<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.9.3">
<l>viṭaiyēḻaṉ ṟaṭarttu vekuṇṭu vilaṅkaluṟa</l>
<l>paṭaiyālā ḻitaṭṭa paramaṉ parañcōti</l>
<l>maṭaiyārnī lamalkum vayalcūḻ kaṇṇapuramoṉ</l>
<l>ṟuṭaiyāṉuk kaṭiyē ṉoruvark kuriyēṉō</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I who am a servant to the one who has the unique [place] Kaṇṇapuram,</l>
<l>Surrounded by fields where lilies abound in full [water] channels,</l>
<l>The celestial light, supreme lord who blocked the sea with an army</l>
<l rend="indent">that pulled up mountains,</l>
<l>Having once raged, crushing seven bulls, am I a possession</l>
<l rend="indent">of someone [else]?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
